If you require a reminder of how to find out who your Personal Tutees are you could check this with your SES team at <a href="mailto:sso@comp.leeds.ac.uk">sso@comp.leeds.ac.uk</a> They should also have highlighted to you if you have any tutees that are under 18, have a disability or require any other specific support.

&nbsp;

You can also follow <a href="https://ses.leeds.ac.uk/info/21800/student_support/836/personal_tutoring">A link to further guidance for signposting students and further resources for Personal Tutors</a> for further advice for directing students for further support.

